{"tid":2383278,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"古代香港　有故事講　元祖太公係1680年左右定居青衣島","createTime":"2021-01-27T20:35:01.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-29T04:25:57.000Z","uid":261647,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"95ad6998d6ce19e70cf1cfc6b0cf85077f78fb52","tid":2383278,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T20:35:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/glocalizedlifestyle/posts/263648641849048\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fglocalizedlifestyle%2Fposts%2F263648641849048&d=LvSu6Mc%2FVB7R449T953cU4bsTeectjBlsojPGUwt5kI%3D&h=077c863c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/glocalizedlifestyle/posts/263648641849048</a><br />\n<br />\n作者：國際化本土日常生活 - Glocalized lifestyle<br />\n<br />\n（有故事講<img src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/t67/1/16/1f64b_1f3fb_200d_2642.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fimages%2Femoji.php%2Fv9%2Ft67%2F1%2F16%2F1f64b_1f3fb_200d_2642.png&h=46b02b6c&s={SIZE}\" />）唔講第二個，我（某啲人口中嘅牛屎佬）嘅父系元祖太公係1680年左右定居荒蕪嘅青衣島<img src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/t4c/1/16/1f642.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fimages%2Femoji.php%2Fv9%2Ft4c%2F1%2F16%2F1f642.png&h=2a329b61&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n英國佔領香港島同九龍半島時候，好多新界島民轉種鴉片&mdash; 無他，個政府山高皇帝遠，管我哋啲海島？<br />\n<br />\n更重要係，英國人唔會管，但係新界島嶼非常接近香港島同廣州市場<br />\n<br />\n古代香港更加係有兩個主要族群之分：客家同蜑家<br />\n<br />\n客家人同蜑家人楚河漢界，一族群佔領土地，一族群佔領海洋：客家人負責喺土地上生產農作物，蜑家人就喺海洋上捕魚同貿易（包括同歐洲人），大家就會喺墟市上買賣，各取所需。<br />\n<br />\n根據家族父老口述歷史，古代講到最富裕嘅，就莫過於元朗一帶嘅原居民，即係鄧達智果邊嘅族群。因為佢哋背山面海，唔單止識得用基圍養魚養蝦，更重要&mdash;&mdash;有種稻米。所以佢哋古代時，應該係全香港最富裕嘅一族。今日大家入到屏山，見到當地甚至有「卜卜齋」學堂供子弟讀書，便可見一斑。<br />\n<br />\n相比之下，分分鐘我太公只不過係家族之中一個離家出走，撈唔掂，漂泊到青衣荒島上，霉過霉啟明嘅忤逆仔。<br />\n<br />\n所以，想像一下，其實香港歷史遠比我哋想像中長遠，有待我哋去發掘考證。<br />\n<br />\n唔，大家有興趣嘅話，我諗可以講多啲 #香港故事<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oc3WABX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Foc3WABX.jpg&h=0923baa8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1298c16dc868a1c43746b9e28ed6759061a05df4","tid":2383278,"uid":109706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T20:36:50.000Z","msg":"interesting"},{"pid":"3ffd506ebeb01e85bb284c0e57a2d8c6788c0199","tid":2383278,"uid":28257,"like":7,"dislike":20,"score":-13,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T21:33:28.000Z","msg":"元朝😑<br />\n<br />\n歸元朝入中史，其實姐係間接成立「中國」五千年文明大一統論"},{"pid":"d2ed911bc71faa80d02651181d8a8b2db9d57109","tid":2383278,"uid":61280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3ffd506ebeb01e85bb284c0e57a2d8c6788c0199","tid":2383278,"uid":28257,"like":7,"dislike":20,"score":-13,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T21:33:28.000Z","msg":"元朝😑<br />\n<br />\n歸元朝入中史，其實姐係間接成立「中國」五千年文明大一統論"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T23:04:49.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">等唔緊要喎，有埋《完朝》歷史就Perfect嗱<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />！！！</span></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"505666e2b8aeb32c457ecdb03d568aca35ca4888","tid":2383278,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T23:06:49.000Z","msg":"古代資產大部份係唔係金？"},{"pid":"778ba502d92333512836a770de775ade3c27436d","tid":2383278,"uid":270703,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"3ffd506ebeb01e85bb284c0e57a2d8c6788c0199","tid":2383278,"uid":28257,"like":7,"dislike":20,"score":-13,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T21:33:28.000Z","msg":"元朝😑<br />\n<br />\n歸元朝入中史，其實姐係間接成立「中國」五千年文明大一統論"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T23:14:43.000Z","msg":"1680年清康熙十九年wow <img src=\"/assets/faces/